  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242187.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>就在更新完Xbox Music应用后，Windows 8/RT下的Xbox Video app也得到了更新，Xbox Video可以整理电脑上的高清影片和电视节目，同时还可以租借或者购买喜欢的电影。</strong>本次升级带来了大量的bug修正和性能提升，同时引入了一个内置搜索的功能，寻找内容及查看新片预告也更为方便，呼声很高的观看记录功能也已经被加入。 </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2daf78c0/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242187.htm&amp;t=Xbox+Video+app+for+Windows+8+%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0+%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242187.htm&amp;t=Xbox+Video+app+for+Windows+8+%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0+%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242187.htm&amp;t=Xbox+Video+app+for+Windows+8+%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0+%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242187.htm&amp;t=Xbox+Video+app+for+Windows+8+%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0+%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242187.htm&amp;t=Xbox+Video+app+for+Windows+8+%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0+%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\"