  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242186.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>现在在Google搜索跟同性恋有关的比如gay、lesbian、lgbt、transgender之类词汇的时候，就会看到如上图的彩蛋，整个搜索框辉煌的变成了彩色横幅，这也是Google一年一度的惯例做法，以表达自己对“同性恋自豪日”的支持。</strong>Google位于旧金山、芝加哥、纽约和都柏林的员工亦会参加<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+LifeatGoogle/posts/ZKd1YHSCiBH\" target=\"_blank\">在6月30日举办的第八届Google同性自豪大游行</a>。 </p> <p> <br /> </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2daf78be/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242186.htm&amp;t=Google+%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A1%86%E5%BD%A9%E8%9B%8B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%AF%B9%E2%80%9C%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%81%8B%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA%E6%97%A5%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242186.htm&amp;t=Google+%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A1%86%E5%BD%A9%E8%9B%8B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%AF%B9%E2%80%9C%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%81%8B%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA%E6%97%A5%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242186.htm&amp;t=Google+%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A1%86%E5%BD%A9%E8%9B%8B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%AF%B9%E2%80%9C%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%81%8B%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA%E6%97%A5%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242186.htm&amp;t=Google+%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%BD%A